headline: NextEra Energy announces participation at the 2025 Wolfe Research Utilities, Midstream & Clean Energy Conference and plans to host an investor conference in December
summary: NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE: NEE) today announced that John Ketchum, chairman, president and chief executive officer, is scheduled to participate in a fireside chat at the 2025 Wolfe Research Utilities, Midstream & Clean Energy Conference in New York City on Wednesday, Oct. 1, 2025, at noon ET. The presentation will include, among other topics, long-term growth-rate expectations for NextEra Energy. headline: NextEra Energy Secures Three Decades More for Point Beach Nuclear
summary: The U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission has approved the subsequent license renewal for NextEra Energy Resources' Point Beach Nuclear Plant Units 1 and 2, securing its operation for approximately three additional decades, with Unit 1 operating through 2050 and Unit 2 through 2053.
